This has been repeated so many times, but it´s the truth: CARROT CAKE. All their slices are pretty big, and my friends have gotten different cakes, such as their cheesecake and chocolate cake. Their service is wonderful, and they speak very good english, so no worries if you have bad Spanish like me. It´s also a good place to study, but it is a little smalll, so don´t expect your own table. If the cafe is full, don´t let that deter you from getting something to go! It´s well worth it.
